# Maps file paths to GitHub teams for automatic PR review requests.
#
# ⚠️  Teams must exist under the @Ascension-EIP org for this to work.
#     If a team doesn't exist yet, GitHub silently ignores the rule.
#     Create teams at: https://github.com/orgs/Ascension-EIP/teams
#
# Squad routing reference:
#   Quentin   → AI / Python      → @Ascension-EIP/ai
#   Renaud    → Rust / API       → @Ascension-EIP/backend
#   Romaric   → Flutter / Mobile → @Ascension-EIP/mobile
#   Arthur    → DevOps / CI      → @Ascension-EIP/devops
#   Alexandra → DB / Infra       → @Ascension-EIP/infra
#   Darius    → Documentation    → @Ascension-EIP/docs
#   Eric      → Architecture     → @Ascension-EIP/leads
#   Ridjan    → Testing          → @Ascension-EIP/testers
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Default: repo owner reviews anything not matched below
*                       @Ascension-EIP/leads

# AI pipeline (Python, PyTorch, MediaPipe, OpenCV)
apps/ai/                @Ascension-EIP/ai

# Backend API (Rust, Axum)
apps/server/            @Ascension-EIP/backend

# Mobile app (Flutter)
apps/mobile/            @Ascension-EIP/mobile

# Documentation
docs/                   @Ascension-EIP/docs

# DevOps & CI/CD
docker-compose.yml      @Ascension-EIP/devops
.github/                @Ascension-EIP/devops
Dockerfile*             @Ascension-EIP/devops

# Infrastructure (DB migrations, queue config, storage)
**/migrations/          @Ascension-EIP/infra

# Tests
apps/**/tests/          @Ascension-EIP/testers
